title: 806. What All 32 Teams Need to Get Accomplished in the Draft
itunes:title: 806. What All 32 Teams Need to Get Accomplished in the Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys discuss how information coming out like medicals can impact a few players' draft stock. Next, the duo rebuild the Jets through the draft. For the rest of the show, the pair go through what all 32 teams need to get accomplished in the draft and also hit on team needs for each team.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
